data.description: Discover this potential filled gem in the heart of Houston's coveted 77026 area. This duplex boasts an unbeatable location, offering a quick commute to Downtown Houston and the convenience of no HOA/POA restrictions.    Both units are already tenant-occupied on flexible month-to-month leases, perfect flexibility for future adjustments.    This property is your blank canvas, ready for a creative touch. Cosmetic updates are needed to transform these units into modern, desirable living spaces. A central HVAC system was just replaced last year, ensuring comfort and efficiency for your occupants.    Buyer should do their own due diligence, as this is an as-is sale. Whether you're an astute investor seeking an income-producing asset or a retail buyer looking for a strategic purchase, this duplex presents a rare opportunity in an excellent location.
